*zenity-2.6.0 (1 Apr 2004)

  01 Apr 2004; foser <foser@gentoo.org> zenity-2.6.0.ebuild :
  Gnome 2.6 final, add patch from 1.8

  22 Mar 2004; L. Boshell <leonardop@gentoo.org> zenity-1.8.ebuild,
  files/zenity-1.8-utf8_fix.patch:
  Patch that prevents codeset conversion to UTF-8 when parsing command
  line arguments. Closes bug #45204.

